snapshots that you can take advantage of, as well as the added benefit of our Posit-built

00:17:51.920 --> 00:17:56.800
binary CRAN packages to make things easier and faster to install in your R environment.

00:17:57.520 --> 00:18:04.079
You can find it out and explore it today at p3m.dev, and definitely reach out to Posit

00:18:04.079 --> 00:18:08.079
if you're interested in learning more about the advanced risk management features we talked about

00:18:08.079 --> 00:18:12.640
today, and how you can bring the power of Posit Package Manager into your own organization.

